{
  "texts": [
    "They use a variety of classification models.",
    "Bansal et al.",
    "[42] applied three distinct morphological approaches to de-haring dermoscopy images.",
    "Since the quality of features influences the performance of a classifier, this study integrated features extracted from dermoscopic images by employing handcrafted (HC) and deep learning models (DLM).",
    "The extraction of features is performed by the ResNet50V2 and Effi-cientNet-B0."
